pp Is Getting Into Digital Payments', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'facebooks-whatsapp-is-getting-into-digital-payments', '', '', '2020-05-26 09:14:01', '2020-05-26 09:14:01', '', 0, 'http://tdi_21_d5c', 0, 'post', '', 0),
