s Stocks Struggle; Pound Climbs: Markets Wrap', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oil-extends-gain-as-stocks-struggle-pound-climbs-markets-wrap-2', '', '', '2020-05-26 09:14:03', '2020-05-26 09:14:03', '', 0, 'http://tdi_32_b44', 0, 'post', '', 0),
