 Estate Market could Crash Thanks to China', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vancouvers-real-estate-market-could-crash-thanks-to-china-2', '', '', '2020-05-26 09:14:05', '2020-05-26 09:14:05', '', 0, 'http://tdi_52_d9c', 0, 'post', '', 0),
