 Desert: Google\'s Oasis for Startups in Dubai', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'developers-in-the-desert-googles-oasis-for-startups-in-dubai', '', '', '2020-05-26 09:14:06', '2020-05-26 09:14:06', '', 0, 'http://tdi_63_1de', 0, 'post', '', 0),
